<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">jer 30:0</span></span>

Overview

[Jer 30:1](../../../bib/kjv/jer030.htm#001.md), God shews Jeremiah the
return of the Jews; [Jer 30:4](../../../bib/kjv/jer030.htm#004.md), After
their trouble they shall have deliverance; [Jer
30:10](../../../bib/kjv/jer030.htm#010.md), He comforts Jacob; [Jer
30:18](../../../bib/kjv/jer030.htm#018.md), Their return shall be gracious;
[Jer 30:23](../../../bib/kjv/jer030.htm#023.md), Wrath shall fall on the
wicked.

